Draft, for initial notetaking, a installation script is planed, to provide 
a .iso installation media (operative system + application) as well as
virtual appliances.

You will need the following perl modules installed, to run OpenQuickIT the
management interface.

	Catalyst::Devel
        Catalyst::Log::Log4perl 
	Catalyst::Plugin::Authentication
	Catalyst::Plugin::Session
	Catalyst::Plugin::Session::State::Cookie
	Catalyst::Plugin::Session::Store::FastMmap  # temporal glue
	Catalyst::Plugin::Unicode
	Catalyst::View::JSON
	Catalyst::View::TT

For devel, the following modules are used.

	Catalyst::Helper::View::JSON
	Catalyst::Helper::View::TT
	Test::Pod::Coverage
